        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1961-01-19T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1961-01-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="62"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d62">
                <head>62. Telegram From [<hi rend="italic">location not declassified</hi>] to the
                    Central Intelligence Agency<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d62fn1">Source:
                        Central Intelligence Agency Files, [<hi rend="italic">text not
                            declassified</hi>], Folder 3. Secret; Routine. Repeated priority to
                        Leopoldville. Received at 0135Z.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<hi rend="italic">location not declassified</hi>],
                            <date calendar="gregorian" when="1961-01-19">January 19,
                        1961</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>0283 [<hi rend="italic">less than 1 line not declassified</hi>]. 1. Thanks for
                    Patrice. If we had known he was coming we would have baked a snake.</p>
                <p>2. Per [<hi rend="italic">name not declassified</hi>] <gloss target="#t_GOK_1"
                        >GOK</gloss> had no advance word whatsoever. <persName corresp="#p_LPE_1"
                        >Lumumba</persName> severely beaten at airport by gendarmerie, then taken
                    Jadotville prison where guarded by all white guards. <gloss target="#t_GOK_1"
                        >GOK</gloss> does not plan liquidate <persName corresp="#p_LPE_1"
                        >Lumumba</persName>. [<hi rend="italic">name not declassified</hi>] fears
                    chances of Balubakat uprising in Eville considerably increased.<note n="2"
                        xml:id="d62fn2">Most of this cable is quoted in <hi rend="italic">Interim
                            Report,</hi> p. 51.</note>
                </p>
                <p>End of message.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
